PKNIC is the .pk domain name registry in the Pakistan, it was started by a Pakistani American Ashar Nisar in June 1992. PKNIC is responsible for the administration of the .PK domain name space, including the operation of the DNS for the Root-Servers for .PK domains, and registration and maintenance of all .PK domain names. The company is operated as a self-supporting organization. "PKNIC" is managed and owned by an American-based company started by a Pakistani American.
